__NOTOC__{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SoundPitch}}void '''A_SoundPitch''' (int ''slot'', double ''pitch'')
==Usage== Sets the pitch of the sound currently playing on the specified [[sound channels|channel]].
===Parameters=== *''slot'': the channel on which the sound is playing. *''pitch'': the pitch value to set.
